{"id":801,"slug":"feast-fable-a-story-cookalong","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/events/feast-fable-a-story-cookalong/","title":"Feast Fable A Story Cookalong","company":"Woodfire Camping x Tale & Hitch","genre":"Children & Young People","description":"Join the Story Baker for a magical, immersive experience as we make and break bread together around the fire. The Story Baker has a wonderful recipe. It’s as old as time, yet it’s still made, every day, in people’s homes the world over. The ingredients? A traditional folk tale with many twists and turns; a willingness to join in (everyone in the audience can participate) and, of course, YOU! Our expert fire chefs from Woodfire Camping will help you cook your creation over the fire before we sit to share and break bread together. This enchanting and hands on show shares traditional tales from around the world and is about cooking, sharing, contributing and friendship. Please read before booking: Due to the nature of this event children must be accompanied by an adult. 1 adult to no more than 2 children. No child under 18 will be admitted unless accompanied by an adult. All ingredients supplied - flour and fire will be present; gluten-free options available.","duration_minutes":60,"age_suitability":"5+","image_url":"https://content.brightonfringe.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/04-20-2026-095842-3717.jpg","website":"","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/brightonfringe/","twitter":"https://twitter.com/brightonfringe","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/brightonfringefestival","accessibility_features":["Wheelchair","Accessible","Assistance Dog"],"content_warnings":[],"cast":[],"scraped_at":"2026-05-19T15:11:14.892975","venue":{"id":36,"slug":"under-the-archway-at-caravanserai-outdoor-stage","name":"Under the Archway at Caravanserai (Outdoor Stage)","address":"North of St Peter's Church, York Place, East Sussex","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/venues/under-the-archway-at-caravanserai-outdoor-stage","lat":50.